    "actions_taken": [
      "Bridge mobilized the Medic",
      "IP taken to rig hospital for evaluation",
      "Leg splinted",
      "Medivac flight arranged"
    ],
    "summary": "On 18-Aug-2015 at approximately 12:45 p.m. onboard the drillship Rowan Relentless, a third party employee sustained a fractured right fibula when a chain fall hook came free from a cuttings box lid and fell uncontrolled onto the injured person's right leg. The incident occurred while the employee was attempting to close a drill cuttings box lid in preparation for helicopter arrival. The chain fall hook lacked a safety clevis (clip), and the employee was working without supervision or assistance.",
